        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1944690408" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13198044894940059603">Human flourishing is embedded in historical traditions, and any total revolution that intends to strip away this necessary embedment is dangerous. Actually, if we strip away historical traditions, Burke believed that there is nothing solid beneath. What is left is sheer violence and beastly force. Progression might not be as desirable as it sounds. Great insight, and highly relevant today!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


